    "content": "<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;box-sizing:inherit;color:rgb(10, 10, 35);font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;font-size:19px;font-stretch:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant-alternates:inherit;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-numeric:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:inherit;margin:0px 0px 1.5em;min-width:100%;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">.<strong>Is JavaScript Weird?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;box-sizing:inherit;color:rgb(10, 10, 35);font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;font-size:19px;font-stretch:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant-alternates:inherit;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-numeric:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:inherit;margin:0px 0px 1.5em;min-width:100%;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">The rumors are that <code style=\"border-width:0px;box-sizing:inherit;font-family:&quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, monospace;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;font-size:0.8em;font-stretch:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-weight:400 !important;line-height:1em;margin:0px;padding:0px 5px 2px;vertical-align:baseline;word-break:normal;\">JavaScript is weird</code>! Well, it can be, especially when you see code like these examples:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-width:0px;box-sizing:inherit;color:var(--gray85);font-family:Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;font-size:1.4rem;font-stretch:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant-alternates:inherit;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-numeric:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-weight:400;hyphens:none;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.5em;margin:1.5em 0px 3em;max-width:100%;min-width:100%;orphans:2;overflow-wrap:normal;overflow:auto;padding:20px;tab-size:4;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-shadow:rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 1px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;widows:2;word-break:normal;word-spacing:0px;\">\n<code class=\"language-plaintext language-js\" style=\"border-width:0px;box-sizing:inherit;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, monospace;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;font-size:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-weight:400 !important;hyphens:none;line-height:inherit;margin:0px;overflow-wrap:normal;padding:0px;tab-size:4;text-align:left;text-shadow:rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 1px;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;word-break:normal;word-spacing:normal;\">+[] == +![]; // returns true\n\nNumber([]); // returns 0\n\nnull &gt;= 0; // returns true\n\n0.1 + 0.2 == 0.3 // Who could believe, it returns fasle!\n\n[10, 1, 3].sort() // Returns, [1, 10, 3]</code></pre>\n<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;box-sizing:inherit;color:rgb(10, 10, 35);font-family:Lato, sans-serif;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;font-size:19px;font-stretch:inherit;font-style:normal;font-variant-alternates:inherit;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-numeric:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:inherit;margin:0px 0px 1.5em;min-width:100%;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">How can you explain these? The only way you can explain these quirks is by explaining their underlying concepts. Besides a few tiny weird things (for example, the type of <code style=\"border-width:0px;box-sizing:inherit;font-family:&quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, monospace;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;font-size:0.8em;font-stretch:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-weight:400 !important;line-height:1em;margin:0px;padding:0px 5px 2px;vertical-align:baseline;word-break:normal;\">null</code> is still an <code style=\"border-width:0px;box-sizing:inherit;font-family:&quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, monospace;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;font-size:0.8em;font-stretch:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-weight:400 !important;line-height:1em;margin:0px;padding:0px 5px 2px;vertical-align:baseline;word-break:normal;\">object</code> in JavaScript), you can explain most syntax by understanding the underlying concepts. You'll need to try doing that to figure out these weird things.</p>"
